<title>USA: Commonwealth Industries files offering.</title>
<headline>Commonwealth Industries files offering.</headline>
<dateline>LOUISVILLE, Ky. 1997-07-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Commonwealth Industries Inc said on Thursday that it had filed a registration statement with the Securities and Exchange Commission for a public offering of five million shares of its common stock.</p>
<p>In a press statement, the company said all the shares would be offered by the company and that Morgan Stanley &amp; Co Inc would act as lead underwriter for the offering.</p>
<p>Commonwealth, an aluminum sheet producer, said proceeds from the offering would reduce debts it incurred in September 1996 with the acquisition of CasTech Aluminum Group Inc.</p>
